' description: hand_off_session baton 接力 sequence — 4 主路径 (cwd 反查 / 双模式分流 / spawn + adopt + task / cleanup)
' last_updated: 2026-05-29
@startuml hand-off-session-flow

title hand_off_session — baton 接力 sequence (4 主路径)

actor Caller as C
participant "hand_off facade" as H
participant "plan resolve\n(plan-driven 才用)" as I
participant "spawn 控制器" as SP
participant "数据表\n(会话 / 团队 / 任务)" as DB
participant "baton 收尾\n(关 teammate + 归档 caller)" as BC
participant "会话管理器 + SDK" as SM

== 入口: 白名单 + cwd 反查 ==

C -> H: invoke(plan_id?, prompt?, cwd?, adapter?, team_name?,\n  adopt_teammates?, archive_caller?, team_task_policy?, ...)
H -> DB: 反查 caller cwd / cwdReleaseMarker
note right of H
  入口拦截器: 白名单 deny external (起 SDK 子进程 fork bomb 风险)
  DB throw / row null → fail-open 退化 + console.warn
end note

== 段 1: 双模式分流 ==

alt plan-driven (plan_id 传)
  H -> I: 解析 plan
  I -> I: 按 fallback 链找 plan 文件 + 校验 + 构造 cold start prompt
  I --> H: { planFilePath, worktreePath, mainRepo, coldStartPrompt }
  H -> H: cwd 默认 = mainRepo (cwd resilience)
else generic (无 plan_id)
  H -> H: 直接组装 generic 上下文 (cold start prompt = args.prompt 或默认)
  H -> H: cwd 默认 = caller cwd (与 plan-driven 不同)
end

H -> H: cwd 兜底链 + 失效自动回退

== 段 2: spawn 新 SDK session + adopt + task 三态 ==

H -> SP: spawn (handOffMode=true → 跳防御 + 不写 spawn-link)
SP -> SM: 起 SDK 子进程
SP --> H: { newSid, teamId?, spawnPromptMessageId? }

opt adopt_teammates=true
  H -> DB: ≥1 lead 硬约束: caller 至少在 1 个 team 是 lead
  H -> DB: 转交 lead 角色 (per team loop, firstTeam 优先)
  note right of DB
    firstTeam swap 失败 → 回滚 newSid + reject
    非 firstTeam 失败 → 软失败继续
  end note
end

opt archive_caller=true (默认)
  H -> DB: 按 team_task_policy 三态过继 task\n(clear-team / preserve-team / skip)
  note right of DB
    reassign throw 仅 warn 不阻塞
  end note
end

== 段 3: baton cleanup (与 archive_plan 共享 helper) ==

H -> BC: runBatonCleanup({callerSid})
opt adopt_teammates=false (默认)
  BC -> SM: phase 1: 关 caller 同 team 全部 teammate\n(excludeSessionIds={newSid} 防 spawn 加入的 newSid 被一并关)
end
opt archive_caller=true (默认)
  BC -> SM: phase 2: 归档 caller session
  note right of SM
    archive throw → archived='failed' warn-only
  end note
end
BC --> H: { teammatesShutdown, archived }

== 段 4: 收口 ok return ==

H --> C: ok({ mode, sessionId, cwd, teamId?, archived, teammatesShutdown,\n  adopted? (preserved/failed/teamsTotal), taskReassignment (status/count/policy) })

@enduml
